      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm looking at making another big transfer to the South Sudan relief fund next week, maybe another $500k. Before I pull the trigger, I just need to be 100% sure about the efficiency. What percentage of my funds actually hits the ground for field ops vs how much gets eaten up by your admin/marketing costs?",
