      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good, but I've seen other NGOs claim similar things and then get hit with scandals about high overhead. A 5% marketing cost seems suspiciously low for an organization of your size. Do you have a specific breakdown or an audit report I can look at that confirms that 95% figure for the South Sudan fund specifically?",
